---
// Mission - Dark blue section with mission statement
---

<section class="relative bg-mission-blue py-20 md:py-28 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-cuidaty-primary/20 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 relative z-10">

    <!-- Main Mission Statement -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-serif text-white leading-tight">
        Acreditamos que o mundo melhora quando cuidamos uns dos outros
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
        E quem cuida, também precisa ser cuidado.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <div class="h-px w-16 bg-secondary"></div>
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="h-px w-16 bg-secondary"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Supporting Content -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-beige rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-cuidaty-dark mb-6 text-center">
          Cuidar de quem cuida começa pela estrutura
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Nossa missão é devolver tempo e tranquilidade para profissionais da saúde através de tecnologia que funciona de verdade.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Quando você tem um sistema que realmente entende suas necessidades, pode focar no que realmente importa: o cuidado genuíno com seus pacientes.
        </p>

        <!-- Values -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-10">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cuidaty-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-cuidaty-dark mb-2">Simplicidade</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Tecnologia intuitiva que não complica</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-cuidaty-dark mb-2">Confiança</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Dados seguros e protegidos</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cuidaty-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-cuidaty-dark mb-2">Empatia</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Construído por quem entende</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
